Privacy Policy
We care about your privacy. Here’s what you need to know:
- Data We Collect: Your name, email, and site usage.
- How We Use It: To improve our services and communicate with you.
- Who We Share With: We don’t sell your info. It’s shared only when necessary.
- Your Rights: Access, correct, or delete your data.
- Security: We protect your info but can’t guarantee complete safety.
